---
import Layout from '../../components/layout/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'April 2024';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Press5.xyz privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="bg-brand-gradient py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100 mt-2">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-gray max-w-none">
      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Press5.xyz is a UK-based hosting provider. We operate this website and provide web hosting, TeamSpeak server hosting, and Discord bot hosting services. References to "we", "us", or "our" in this policy refer to Press5.xyz.</p>

      <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect the following types of data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> your name, email address, and message content when you contact us.</li>
        <li><strong>Hosting account data:</strong> name, email, and billing address when you sign up for a hosting service.</li>
        <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> IP addresses and request logs generated by your use of our hosting services.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> essential session cookies only. We do not use tracking or analytics cookies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We use collected data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to contact form enquiries</li>
        <li>Provision and manage your hosting services</li>
        <li>Send service-related communications (e.g. invoices, outage notifications)</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your data to third parties. We do not use your data for advertising.</p>

      <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain account data for as long as your account is active and for up to 7 years thereafter for legal and accounting purposes. Contact form enquiries are retained for 12 months.</p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights (UK GDPR)</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>

      <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>This website uses essential cookies only (e.g. to remember your session if logged into a client area). We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any third-party tracking cookies.</p>

      <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — for sending transactional emails in response to contact form submissions.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — for CDN, DDoS protection, and DNS. Cloudflare may process IP addresses.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: #111827; }
  .prose p, .prose li { color: #374151; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prose a { color: #2563EB; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
